#MEM id=pre-dev-delivery-planning source=/root/yvon/agent-department/COO/diana/skills/marketplace/pre-dev-delivery-planning/SKILL.md savings=6%
M||tx|---
M||name|ring:pre-dv-delivery-planning
M||desc|\|
M||Gate|Delivery roadmap and timeline planning.
M||tx|Transforms tasks into realistic delivery schedule w/ ct path al,
M||tx|resource allocation, and delivery breakdown. MANDATORY gate for both workflows.
M||tx|---
M|When|it|Tasks passed Gate 7 validation (Full Track) OR Gate 3 (Small Track)
M|When|it|Need realistic delivery timeline w/ dates
M|When|it|Ready to convert tasks into delivery schedule
M|When|it|Team composition known or determinable
M|Skip|it|Tasks not validated → complete task breakdown first
M|Skip|it|Proof-of-concept w/o delivery commitment
M|Skip|it|Research/exploration work w/o delivery deadline
M|Sequ|**Ru|** ring:dv-cycle
M|Sequ|**Ru|** ring:pre-dv-task-breakdown, ring:pre-dv-subtask-creation
M|Sequ|tx|Every roadmap must be grounded in reality, not optimism. Tasks not validated, team composition unknown, or start date absent → STOP and gather the missing input before proceeding.
M|Phas|tx|\| Phase \| Activities \|
M|Phas|tx|\|-------\|------------\|
M|Phas|tx|\| **1. Input Gathering** \| Load tasks.md; ask us for start date, team composition, delivery cadence, period cfg, velocity multiplier \|
M|Phas|tx|\| **2. Dependency al** \| bd dependency graph, identify ct path, find parallelization opportunities \|
M|Phas|tx|\| **3. Capacity Planning** \| Calculate team velocity (custom multiplier), allocate resources, identify bottlenecks \|
M|Phas|tx|\| **4. Delivery Breakdown** \| Group tasks by cadence (sprint/cycle/continuous), calculate period boundaries, identify spill overs, map parallel streams \|
M|Phas|tx|\| **5. Risk al** \| Flag hi-risk dependencies, add contingency buffer (10-20%), define mitigations \|
M|Phas|tx|\| **6. Gate Validation** \| Verify all tasks scheduled, ct path correct, dates achievable, period boundaries respected \|
M|Q1: |When|YYYY-MM-DD
M|Q2: |How |1 (solo), 2 (pair), 3-4 (squad), 5+ (large team)
M|Q3: |Opti|Sprints (1-2 weeks), Cycles (1-3 months), Continuous (no fixed intervals)
M|Q4 (|- Du|1w, 2w, 1mo, 2mo, 3mo
M|Q4 (|- St|YYYY-MM-DD
M|Q5: |tx|\| Option \| Multiplier \| Example \|
M|Q5: |tx|\|--------\|-----------\|---------\|
M|Q5: |tx|\| Minimal validation \| 1.2x \| 4h AI → 4.8h adjusted \|
M|Q5: |tx|\| Standard validation ← recommended \| 1.5x \| 4h AI → 6.0h adjusted \|
M|Q5: |tx|\| Deep validation \| 2.0x \| 4h AI → 8.0h adjusted \|
M|Q5: |tx|\| Heavy rework \| 2.5x \| 4h AI → 10.0h adjusted \|
M|Q5: |tx|\| Custom \| us-specified \| — \|
M|Velo|tx|```
M|Velo|tx|adjusted_hours = ai_estimate × multiplier
M|Velo|tx|calendar_hours = adjusted_hours ÷ 0.90
M|Velo|tx|calendar_days  = calendar_hours ÷ 8 ÷ team_size
M|Velo|tx|task_days      = calendar_days + taura_days
M|Velo|Wher|
M|Velo|tx|ai_estimate = from tasks.md (AI-ag-hours)
M|Velo|tx|0.90        = capacity utilization (AI ag standard)
M|Velo|tx|taura_days  = 0 (dv/Delivery) \| 5 (qual) \| 10 (qual integration)
M|Velo|tx|```
M|Peri|For |`task_end_date <= period_end_date`
M|Peri|it|If yes → fits completely (✅)
M|Peri|- If|allocate days split across periods
M|Peri|Cont|no period boundaries — tasks scheduled by dependency and capacity only.
M|Crit|tx|1. bd dependency graph from tasks.md
M|Crit|tx|2. Calculate Earliest Start Date (ESD) per task
M|Crit|tx|3. Calculate Latest Start Date (LSD) w/o delaying project
M|Crit|tx|4. Tasks where ESD = LSD → on ct path (zero slack)
M|Outp|MUST|
M|Outp|it|`doc/pre-dv/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.md` — human-readable
M|Outp|it|`doc/pre-dv/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.json` — machine-readable (see sc below)
M|Outp|**To|**
