M|Outp|tx|\| monorepo \| Index + per-md `{md.path}/doc/pre-dv/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.{md,json}` \|
M|Outp|tx|\| multi-repo \| Per-repo `{repo.path}/doc/pre-dv/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.{md,json}` \|
