M|JSON|tx|1. `dates.startDate` and `dates.endDate` REQUIRED — not null
M|JSON|tx|2. `tasks` array MUST have ≥1 item
M|JSON|tx|3. Every task MUST have `id`, `description`, `aiEstimate`, `adjusted`, `calendar`, `days`
M|JSON|tx|4. `confidenceScore` MUST be 0-100
M|JSON|tx|5. `milestones` MUST have ≥1 item
M|JSON|tx|6. `criticalPath.taskIds` MUST reference valid task IDs
M|JSON|tx|7. `version` MUST be `"1.0.0"`
M|JSON|tx|8. `milestones[].taskIds` and `spillOvers` MUST reference valid task IDs
M|JSON|tx|9. `velocity.teamSize` > 0
M|JSON|tx|10. `cycleCapacity` MUST be present w/ all 5 fields
M|JSON|tx|11. `cycleCapacity.availableDays` = `grossDays - bugBufferDays`
M|JSON|tx|12. `cycleCapacity.slackDays` = `availableDays - allocatedDays` (negative = over-committed → add risk)
M|JSON|13. |0 for dv/delivery, 5 or 10 for qual
M|JSON|14. |`periodDuration` = null, `periodStartDate` = null, milestones tp = `milestone`, spillOvers = `[]`
M|Gate|tx|\| Category \| Requirements \|
M|Gate|tx|\|----------\|--------------\|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Input Completeness** \| Start date, team composition, cadence, period config (if sprint/cycle), velocity multiplier all confirmed \|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Dependency al** \| Graph built, ct path identified, parallel streams defined, no circular deps \|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Capacity Planning** \| Velocity calculated, resources allocated, bottlenecks identified, ≤80% utilization \|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Delivery Breakdown** \| Periods match cadence, boundaries calculated, spill overs identified, delivery goals measurable \|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Risk Management** \| hi-risk deps flagged, buffer added (10-20%), mitigations defined \|
M|Gate|tx|\| **Timeline Realism** \| No best-case assumptions, ct path validated, dates achievable \|
M|Gate|**Ga|** ✅ PASS → Ready for execution \| ⚠️ CONDITIONAL (adjust) \| ❌ FAIL (rework)
M|Conf|tx|\| Factor \| Points \| Criteria \|
M|Conf|tx|\|--------\|--------\|----------\|
M|Conf|| De|30, Most clear: 20, Ambiguous: 10 \|
M|Conf|| Ca|25, Optimistic (90%+): 10, Undefined: 0 \|
M|Conf|| Cr|25, Partial: 15, Assumptions: 5 \|
M|Conf|| Ri|20, Some: 10, None: 0 \|
M|Conf|Scor|proceed w/ confidence. 50-79: flag assumptions. <50: resolve unknowns before committing dates.